        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2346",
        "content": "If we have to die, I would rather do so moving; but I don't believe that we shall die.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2346_152201_000001_000000",
